Are you ready for the adventure?

. For the rest of your life, you may be torn between suffering the fate of reproduction and facing your true self, wandering through the night. But you still really want a child so badly.
You've been confused, you've fought, but in the end you haven't beaten the constraints of social rules and the desire for the next generation.
You keep on and on tearing your soul apart in this pain.
